Package: localvar
Title: Local Volatility Analysis with Sliding Window Approaches
Version: 2.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Diemithry", "Kloppenburg", , "diemithrykloppenburg@hotmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An R package for analyzing local volatility patterns in data using 
    sliding window approaches and reliability zone estimation. Optimized for 
    memory-efficient analysis on Mac M3 systems with comprehensive batch processing
    and visualization capabilities.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
